paper_metadata.title: MAIN TEXT
paper_metadata.extraction_summary: The paper discusses the effects of various β-blockers on HERG channels, specifically focusing on mutations Y652A and F656C in the KCNH2 gene. No specific genetic variants in KCNH2 with penetrance data were reported.

challenges: The paper did not provide specific genetic variant data for KCNH2 with penetrance information.
extraction_metadata.notes: The paper focused on the functional effects of β-blockers on HERG channels and did not report individual genetic variants with clinical or penetrance data.
